inspection_findings.text:
The provider was out of compliance with this rule on 2 separate occasions by;
1. Multiple staff members failing to treat clients with dignity . During the investigation inspection, multiple interviews disclosed that staff yell at, swear at, and make belittling comments to some clients. During the investigation inspection, interviews substantiated that some staff members yell at and antagonize clients. It was reported that some staff members tell clients to “shut the fuck up”, 
2. A staff member causing potential harm and acts of violence. During an investigation inspection, multiple interviews substantiated that a staff member made verbal threats to a client and punched a hole in a hallway wall.
